ttps://na.cx/i/8pAyEOY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8pAyEOY.jpg&h=6abdede8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[ 備戰 ] 夢境作戰訓話 + 整合Post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1267323/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1267323/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人到而家仲未識真正咁運用三角鐵馬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1267307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1267307</a>"},{"pid":"a350687324e6615a1f39b5466a8cbf5ef116b91f","tid":1268490,"uid":53811,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T11:39:29.000Z","msg":"mon post的阿sir們<br />\n<br />\n睇下邊個先係真暴徒啦<br />\n<br />\n反送中示威者頂多就圍下警總，拆下招牌，掟下雞蛋，可能有少少碰撞，你成身有pad怕乜呀，小事啦，你頂多企下辛苦下唔夠訓姐<br />\n<br />\n就算我地係反對警察都未去到呢個地步啦，都係想有返個裁決還你地同義士清白呀<br />\n<br />\n所謂撐警粉絲，佢地分分鐘細個果陣文革打死過唔少人，老師校長乜人都比佢地拉去打拉去殺，唔係以為佢地一起手會放過你下話<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">比呢班人得勢，連你地都拉去處決呀</span></strong><br />\n話就話黑警，都係香港市民一部分呀<br />\n頂多有錯咪上法庭囉，都不至於死啦<br />\n唔想死就自己諗下應該點做啦"},{"pid":"0dbb3304a3c1060cabeecf9d6e4f86ca0fe96614","tid":1268490,"uid":119283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T11:41:30.000Z","msg":"推爆"},{"pid":"94882f5b51bc6840a84d42e928d69ab67739e4a4","tid":1268490,"uid":124618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T11:47:06.000Z","msg":"七一見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ONe7MbZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FONe7MbZ.png&h=14f2ed61&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9a01b2df37b47a91191e4ee8a574f4f484517b6","tid":1268490,"uid":255690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T11:48:03.000Z","msg":"第二日出報紙 話班狗以怨報德"},{"pid":"3b3a11f7183550fd3348504f2a808163a37396a7","tid":1268490,"uid":269217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"465deac0723d968be8586dc12d485bda4f29628e","tid":1268490,"uid":156666,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d4